[The 90-second teaser war hasn't ended]

4
00:00:23,801 --> 00:00:25,781
The No. 1 short drama director.

5
00:00:25,781 --> 00:00:27,241
AI creator.

6
00:00:27,241 --> 00:00:29,281
I'm the Bong Joon Ho of the BL, Yang Gyeong Hee.

7
00:00:29,281 --> 00:00:30,781
I'm a 10-million short drama director.

8
00:00:30,781 --> 00:00:33,501
