10
00:00:37,451 --> 00:00:39,411
[What's this?]

11
00:00:39,411 --> 00:00:41,441
I saw a director for the first time today.

12
00:00:41,441 --> 00:00:43,991
It's the best compliment to directors.

13
00:00:43,991 --> 00:00:45,661
[And]

14
00:00:45,661 --> 00:00:47,921
[There were two eliminations]

15
00:00:47,921 --> 00:00:50,121
