183
00:08:49,891 --> 00:08:52,601
He's been imprisoned in one place.

184
00:08:52,601 --> 00:08:55,511
You see blood on his hands and feet.

185
00:08:55,511 --> 00:09:00,271
I'll make sure he looks convincingly possessed.

186
00:09:01,521 --> 00:09:03,171
[What's "The Archangel's Visit" like?]

187
00:09:03,171 --> 00:09:06,211
Scream while holding the Bible.

188
00:09:06,211 --> 00:09:09,701
The archangel visits the home of a thug

189
00:09:09,701 --> 00:09:12,111
who hasn't found his purpose in life.

190
00:09:12,111 --> 00:09:14,481
He gains the ability to see spirits.

191
00:09:14,481 --> 00:09:19,991
He becomes a powerful exorcist in the end.

192
00:09:19,991 --> 00:09:21,971
[The long-awaited exorcism scene]

193
00:09:21,971 --> 00:09:23,831
[Totally into it]

194
00:09:26,771 --> 00:09:28,461
Cut! Okay.

195
00:09:28,461 --> 00:09:31,341
[Is she satisfied with the scene?]

196
00:09:31,341 --> 00:09:33,461
[And]

197
00:09:34,321 --> 00:09:37,291
[Another killer cameo appearance]

198
00:09:38,651 --> 00:09:42,591
[The cameos have been leaving strong impressions]

199
00:09:42,591 --> 00:09:45,161
[Actor Lee Hyo Jung]

200
00:09:45,161 --> 00:09:46,921
[Actor Ko Chang Seok]

201
00:09:46,921 --> 00:09:50,811
[Actress Shin Ye Eun]

202
00:09:51,571 --> 00:09:54,101
[The special cameo in this occult short is?]

203
00:09:54,101 --> 00:09:57,691
